{#
    Qui Sommes-Nous Section — Clean, modern layout with building image
#}

<section style="padding: 1rem 0 4rem 0; background-color: #ffffff; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 4rem;">

            {# Left: Text Content #}
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 320px; max-width: 450px;">
                
                {# Eyebrow label #}
                <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem; background-color: #F8F9FA; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
                    <p style="color: #6B7280; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin: 0;">Notre entreprise</p>
                </div>

                {# Headline #}
                <h2 style="
                    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
                    font-weight: 800;
                    color: #111827;
                    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
                    line-height: 1.1;
                    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
                ">Qui sommes-nous&nbsp;?</h2>

                {# Decorative Line #}
                <div style="width: 60px; height: 4px; background-color: #E87722; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-radius: 2px;"></div>

                {# Body text #}
                <p style="
                    font-size: 1.1rem;
                    color: #4B5563;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
                ">
                    Ouvert depuis 2003, Catéco est l'enseigne incontournable des guyanais dans l'équipement
                    des maisons, bricolage, jardinage et loisirs et tant d'autres secteurs. C'est le magasin
                    des bonnes affaires qui propose toujours des prix agressifs. Son catalogue 124&nbsp;pages
                    renouvelé régulièrement propose les produits les plus astucieux et malins.
                </p>

                {# CTA Button #}
                <a href="{{ path('app_about_us') }}"
                   style="
                       display: inline-flex;
                       align-items: center;
                       gap: 0.8rem;
                       background-color: #E87722;
                       color: #ffffff;
                       font-weight: 700;
                       font-size: 1rem;
                       padding: 1rem 2.2rem;
                       border-radius: 8px;
                       text-decoration: none;
                       box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.06);
                       transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
                   "
                   onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#d46517'; this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 15px -3px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.2), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.1)'"
                   onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#E87722'; this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 6px -1px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.06)'">
                    En savoir plus
                    <svg style="width:18px;height:18px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>

            {# Right: Building Image #}
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 320px; max-width: 500px; position: relative;">
                
                {# Image container with modern styling and increased height #}
                <div style="
                    position: relative;
                    border-radius: 16px;
                    overflow: hidden;
                    height: 350px;
                    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
                    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
                "
                onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.03) translateY(-10px)'"
                onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1) translateY(0)'">
                    <img src="{{ asset('assets/shop/images/cateco_cayenne.png') }}"
                         alt="Catéco Building"
                         style="width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; object-fit: cover;">
                    
                    {# Subtle gradient overlay at the bottom for image depth #}
                    <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 0%, transparent 30%); pointer-events: none;"></div>
                </div>

                {# Decorative background accent #}
                <div style="
                    position: absolute;
                    bottom: -20px;
                    right: -20px;
                    width: 70%;
                    height: 70%;
                    background-color: #F3F4F6;
                    border-radius: 16px;
                    z-index: -1;
                "></div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
